Bootstrap: docker
From: ubuntu:18.04

%labels
MAINTAINER darachm

%help

    This container is for providing a python3 environment, as Darach likes it
    for some bioinformatics. Expect this to grow as more stuff is used.
    
    For options, do:

        singularity run this-container-name -h

%files

%post

    apt-get -y update
    apt-get -y install python3 python3-biopython python3-pip

    pip3 install regex numpy pandas jellyfish

%test

    /usr/bin/python3 -V


